can be the roughest seas in the world.

00:04:27.029 --> 00:04:31.010
They can have
60-foot seas here; this time we were lucky,

00:04:31.010 --> 00:04:32.590
but you can
get seasick.

00:04:32.590 --> 00:04:36.499
