00:05:25.889 --> 00:05:27.419
But you
know I was at the bottom of the world and

00:05:27.419 --> 00:05:29.789
I thought
maybe a 15-millimeter full frame fish eye

00:05:29.789 --> 00:05:33.490
lens would
help tell the story about being at the bottom

00:05:33.490 --> 00:05:34.490
