going to need speakers at Google anymore,

00:40:07.870 --> 00:40:09.970
just do
searches move to histogram to the right.

00:40:09.970 --> 00:40:12.760
So anyway, you
want to move the histogram to the right.

00:40:12.760 --> 00:40:13.850
You don't want
that spike.

00:40:13.850 --> 00:40:18.210
If that spike is right to the edge here,
you're going to lose detail.

00:40:18.210 --> 00:40:21.150
